ime":"2017-12-02T03:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想問植物人點申請抽中銀鈔㗎？</blockquote><br />\n又問</blockquote><br />\n你有答咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2c9606b0724e459c1275e7a1c5602969f4d77d","tid":486511,"uid":116905,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:49:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老豆咁嘅情況係慘，但中銀一早就講哂規矩點玩，你自己唔睇又怪得邊個？更何況你明知你老豆行動唔方便，點解唔申請既時候打去問定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撚知啲規條咁on9呀<br />\n又要請假又要山長水遠又要限時咁去拎<br />\n又要親自取又要唔比退<br />\n撚狗咁撚"},{"pid":"32ceab7fb960af8ede841e0d294d5e9a111caeaf","tid":486511,"uid":51215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"申請可以授權其他人申請但拎就唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccfec9909492f34e29e9ba97b869ae165e990c6","tid":486511,"uid":127500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Molamola<br />\n連登仔一面倒支持on9中銀</blockquote><br />\n見到你先覺得連登molamola"},{"pid":"20bf335918553fdb278df60593f5b5659e9eed15","tid":486511,"uid":116905,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:49:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.bochk100.com/faq_c.jsp#qa6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bochk100.com%2Ffaq_c.jsp%23qa6&d=Mqva%2FuzIZq0EH9%2BEaea77MmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=80dab202\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bochk100.com/faq_c.jsp#qa6</a><br />\n其實第12同24條都講左<br />\n第12條雖然無涵樓主既特別情況<br />\n但24條已經講左申請者親身領鈔<br />\n因此申請人有必要考量到時係咪可以親身去拎<br />\n所以樓主家父既情況我都覺得係好兩難<br />\n大家向來都有幫朋友 親戚報呢樣個樣<br />\n最係都係被申請者出現先算數<br />\n差別在個活動接唔接受咁樣<br />\n好似今次係唔接受自然有相應既措施<br />\n原意係杜絕炒風又好乜都好<br />\n白紙黑字有晒規矩<br />\n樓主係咁屌我覺得有欠公允<br />\n樓主家父既情況我係同情<br />\n但殘疾人士唔代表可以唔守規矩<br />\n如果中銀特別處理就最好 唔得都無得怪人<br />\n<br />\n我認真鳥 負評我留既<br />\n利申 冇直接間接參與中銀今次鈔票活動</blockquote><br />\n好喇威喇叻喇識中文喇勁勁子呀"},{"pid":"2a8a6ec62781e944737170e455ff31d96930369d","tid":486511,"uid":116905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登終於出潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個植物人老竇比連登仔屌緊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6d3ac725e0dc92dc7f9555eb160364486373ee","tid":486511,"uid":15887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.bochk100.com/faq_c.jsp#qa6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bochk100.com%2Ffaq_c.jsp%23qa6&d=Mqva%2FuzIZq0EH9%2BEaea77MmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=80dab202\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bochk100.com/faq_c.jsp#qa6</a><br />\n其實第12同24條都講左<br />\n第12條雖然無涵樓主既特別情況<br />\n但24條已經講左申請者親身領鈔<br />\n因此申請人有必要考量到時係咪可以親身去拎<br />\n所以樓主家父既情況我都覺得係好兩難<br />\n大家向來都有幫朋友 親戚報呢樣個樣<br />\n最係都係被申請者出現先算數<br />\n差別在個活動接唔接受咁樣<br />\n好似今次係唔接受自然有相應既措施<br />\n原意係杜絕炒風又好乜都好<br />\n白紙黑字有晒規矩<br />\n樓主係咁屌我覺得有欠公允<br />\n樓主家父既情況我係同情<br />\n但殘疾人士唔代表可以唔守規矩<br />\n如果中銀特別處理就最好 唔得都無得怪人<br />\n<br />\n我認真鳥 負評我留既<br />\n利申 冇直接間接參與中銀今次鈔票活動</blockquote><br />\n好喇威喇叻喇識中文喇勁勁子呀</blockquote><br />\n講到白曬其實你靜喺可以屌柒中銀無同情心同聽電話果個on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實講真就咁睇你都無乜可以搞大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上嚟喺咁易屌吓算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4dfa43ced1125c92f0b49dea9a98e28be9a07a0","tid":486511,"uid":116905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:53:51.000Z","