/>\n講到白曬其實你靜喺可以屌柒中銀無同情心同聽電話果個on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實講真就咁睇你都無乜可以搞大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上嚟喺咁易屌吓算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中銀熱線果個男人接線生<br />\n我無屌佢"},{"pid":"5738cb03578b6239be17345b3ef7a41b2b113edc","tid":486511,"uid":116905,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主作篇懶係好笑但係又冇人笑得出既潮文係咩心態？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吓唔撚係掛<br />\n你覺得佢個回覆好笑過我篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cdf11113e9b4932cde6a62998b8f02745d3760","tid":486511,"uid":32979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登終於出潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個植物人老竇比連登仔屌緊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搞清楚啲係屌你，從來冇人屌你啊爸"},{"pid":"3e3b3b19dd7e02a0c535a732c336f736c56a04bf","tid":486511,"uid":116905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>申請可以授權其他人申請但拎就唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登既清泉終於出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有多啲呢位巴打既級數<br />\n咁連登就可以高質返啲<br />\n多謝你呀9527<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ador